description: A comprehensive set of extensions methods to complement Cuemon .NET Framework.
releaseNotes:
This release contains some complimentary extension methods and removal of earlier.
The following work was completed for this release:

- New extensions for Stream: Compress
- New extensions for NameValueCollection: ToWebHeaderCollection
- New extensions for Type: ToFriendlyName
- New extensions for Assembly: GetAssemblyVersion
- New extensions for IEnumerable{TSource}: SelectOne
- New extensions for String: ToTextReader

- Renamed extensions for Uri: GetProtectedUri -> ToProtectedUri, ParseProtectedUri -> VerifyProtectedUri
- Renamed extensions for Stream: Copy (void) -> CopyTo

- Removed extensions for DateTime: GetLowest, GetHighest (due to noise)
- Removed extensions for Object: GetObjectHierarchy (due to noise)
- Removed extensions for IEnumerable: Count, Any (due to noise)
summary: A free and flexible assembly package, built to extend and boost your codebelt - providing vast ways of possibilities for all breeds of coders, programmers, developers and the likes thereof.
title: Cuemon .NET Framework Extensions
